How to exchange/buy/sell things
################################

1. If you want to exchange or buy something; first thing you will need is MONEY:

2. You can get Money by: 

> Digging or placing blocks

> Setting  up a shop or vending machine (you will need to craft it first)

> Buy a shop from other players (see shopping areas)

3. If you need ITEMS, you can BUY them at shops (from players) or from our friendly Iron-Man-NPC at spawn.

4. With a barter table you can also exchange things directly with players.

See Also: [Main] [Shopping Areas]
